name: DSCI551_Foundation-of-Data-Management
description: DSCI 551 – Foundations of Data Management: Focused on database design, SQL, data integrity, and performance optimization, emphasizing scalable and efficient data management practices.

name: Car-Crash-Detection
description: This project uses the YOLOv8 object detection model to automatically detect car crashes from pre-recorded videos. By analyzing frames from annotated video data, the model identifies and highlights crash incidents, helping in post-accident analysis and safety assessments.

name: Electricity-Demand-Forecasting-with-LSTM-SARSA
description: This project explores hybrid approaches for forecasting electricity demand using: 1. Deep Learning (LSTM) — to capture time-series dependencies and predict future demand   2. Reinforcement Learning (SARSA) — to optimize decision-making based on demand forecasts
